ans in which to provide us (humans) a more accurate understanding of world-events and circumstances felt by humans, via our \u2018world wide web\u2019."), mdx("p", null, "**# Linked-Data, Ontologies and Verifiable Claims  "), mdx("p", null, "By:\xA0 ", mdx("a", {
